title "Remote Session Flow"
direction TB
theme light

client Browser "Browser"
gateway GW "API Gateway"
service HUB "Agent Hub"
service Agent "Agent"
external RLY "TURN Relay"

Browser -> GW : POST /api/sessions

GW -> HUB : start session
HUB -> Agent : StartSession command

Agent -> Agent : prepare capture/PTY

Browser <-> GW : WebSocket signaling
GW <-> HUB : signal forwarding
HUB <-> Agent : ICE candidates

Browser <-> RLY : WebRTC media
Agent <-> RLY : WebRTC media
